game.name: Elsa And Anna Paris Shopping
game.description:
This time you will have fun in a unique style and that too with your favorite princesses Anna and Elsa! These two princesses reached Paris last night by a plane. After having a long and healthy sleep, they have awoken early in the morning today and planning to go for shopping. However, suddenly rain got started, but they are determined enough to leave their home for the nearby shopping mall. Will help them pick some rainy clothes? Join Elsa and Anna Paris Shopping game and be prepared to shop together with these two popular princesses!

It is raining outside everywhere in the city and you are their only hope to shop for their desirable dresses, cute umbrellas, fashion bags and shoes, hats and more in this brand new dressing game for girls. Make sure to choose the products that are suitable for walking in the rain. Do not spend all the money on a wider range of only one product. Otherwise you would not have enough cash to purchase other useful items in this one of the best girls games. 

Choose the girl and start shopping with her by clicking on the showroom you want! By clicking the left arrow, you will find a wide collection of hats, shoes, and umbrellas. And, you will find different varieties of shorts, t-shirts and tops, frocks and gowns when you click the arrow that you see on the right side of the screen. Help Elsa select the wonderful outfit option and then you guide Anna to choose a fine rainy dress in this html5 princess doll game!
